					<description><![CDATA[Hello, using the present progressive tense in „I‘m looking forward…“ indicates doing something now. „I look forward…“ means that I am generally and constantly looking forward to hearing from someone. That’s why I would use the latter form!]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Hello, using the present progressive tense in „I‘m looking forward…“ indicates doing something now. „I look forward…“ means that I am generally and constantly looking forward to hearing from someone. That’s why I would use the latter form!</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
